1 tin Pineapple Slices
1 packet Toasted Vanilla Almond Muesli
1 packet Original Thick & Creamy Yoghurt

Drain pineapple slices. Heat a large frying pan over high heat. Cook pineapple until charred, 2-3 minutes
each side.

In a serving bowl, add a layer of toasted vanilla almond muesli (store leftover muesli in an airtight container).

Roughly chop charred pineapple. Add a dollop of original thick & creamy yoghurt to the bowl. Top with pineapple.

FRESH TIP: Heat a frying pan over medium-high heat. Toast some shredded coconut until golden, 2-3 minutes and sprinkle over!